    "The pre-processing steps follow the following steps: a.",
    "Regular expressions We examined the extracted text for recurring patterns of: • Page numbers • Page headers • New page characters • Footnotes • URLs • Subsequent whitespace characters, which we remove using appropriate regular expressions. b.",
